## Development

### Installing python dependencies
```shell
poetry install
```

### Running Tests
```shell
pytest .
```

### Formatting Code
```shell
bash .github/format.sh
```

### Linting
```shell
bash .github/check_lint.sh
```

## Running the Program
On your terminal, run:
```
poetry shell
run-portrayt
```
